sionally use it on keep and relic doors as the 3 part chain was slightly more end then 3 snowblinds but the final style did enough damage to make up for it.   But in combat with actual people, never. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=sloughwi>sloughwi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Initiate</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#000000>(6/16/03 4:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=112.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Styles</span><hr size=1> Interesting...so would it be logical to have Scathing Blade and Decaying Rage replaced with a nice 2-chain side style?<br>
